Or an use Abbot script that looks like this:

&lt;AWTTestScript desc=&quot;Make option pane go away&quot;&gt;
   &lt;component id=&quot;OK&quot; class=&quot;javax.swing.JButton&quot; tag=&quot;OK&quot;/&gt;
   &lt;wait method=&quot;FrameShowing&quot; args=&quot;My Option Title&quot;/&gt;
   &lt;action method=&quot;Click&quot; args=&quot;OK&quot;/&gt;
   &lt;wait method=&quot;!FrameShowing&quot; args=&quot;My Option Title&quot;/&gt;
&lt;/AWTTestScript&gt;

